-- ISDA to Rule Whether Sino-Forest in Bankruptcy Credit Event
-- B y   A b i g a i l   M o s e s
-- 2012-04-02T10:22:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-02/isda-to-rule-whether-sino-forest-in-bankruptcy-credit-event.html
The International Swaps &
Derivatives Association said it will rule if there has been a
bankruptcy credit event that would trigger credit-default swaps
on  Sino-Forest Corp. (TRE)   To contact the reporter on this story:
